{"tid":485883,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到麗瑤下面咁闊","createTime":"2017-12-01T10:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T19:44:49.000Z","uid":7628,"like":353,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5749c2573170526d43244597b0752c4bbc99729","tid":485883,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"估唔到麗瑤邨下面有咁多設施<br />\n又有街市又有小學又有商場<br />\n雖然下面有啲臭 可能係街市啲魚腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/184111_8f531e3f00d94c62a65dcdc85f5be3e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F184111_8f531e3f00d94c62a65dcdc85f5be3e0.jpg&h=12f63ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麗瑤邨位於葵涌第11C區，建在下葵涌一處陡峭的山坡上，鄰近青山公路葵涌段。麗瑤邨是按前香港屋宇建設委員會的規格與標準興建，是首個獲得煤氣供應的公共屋邨[2]。邨內原有3座24層高雙塔式大廈（樂瑤樓、富瑤樓、貴瑤樓）及1座12層高舊長型大廈（華瑤樓），華瑤樓更是70年代公屋中罕有地在各單位備配備兩個梗房與浴缸的房委會公屋大廈，這4座在1976至1977年期間落成。麗瑤邨是荃灣新市鎮首條擁有雙塔式大廈的公共屋邨，大廈單位較舊式屋邨寬敞，很多住戶都願由舊型屋邨調遷至該邨，所以該邨對於減輕當時舊型屋邨的居住擠迫情況，佔有重要地位。"},{"pid":"977ba267d5acaef3731a1610fd9c0cfe8eabfed1","tid":485883,"uid":28301,"like":81,"dislike":363,"score":-282,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:58:58.000Z","msg":"連登真係多On9小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ad6279171f32f87772933a4a36e0b4c6232006","tid":485883,"uid":10793,"like":135,"dislike":3,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"題文相符，正評，上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e566cb562404ebf1256e5672ef8a3f048b46068","tid":485883,"uid":53023,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"佢下面真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n闊過西隧"},{"pid":"bb184b858b8ed7a555a4ff575a03b53d6a88605b","tid":485883,"uid":7628,"like":86,"dislike":5,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登真係多On9小學雞<img